Class AttributesTable<K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.helixsoft.util.AttributesTable<K>

  • public class AttributesTable<K>
extends java.lang.Object
    2D map of attributes An attribute is a (String, Object) pair. Each pair is associated with a Key of any type.

    Could be used to store attributes for Nodes or Edges in a graph.
